  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "In the game your objective is to gather as much money as possible, inorder
    to do that you must connect the facilities to the city/cities, put down vehicles,
    roads, bus stops and traffic lights. The vehicles transport the resources and
    the people, for every delivery money is added to the balance.\nDelivery routes:\n\tFacility
    \u2014> City : (Commodity)\n\t\tsteel \u2014> city\n\t\tpaper \u2014> city\n\t\tfood
    \u2014> city\n\tFacility \u2014> Facility : (Commodity)\n\t\tiron \u2014> steel\n\t\twood
    \u2014> paper\n\tBus Stop \u2014> City : (People)\n\tCity \u2014> City : (People)\nIt's
    important to keep the satisfaction (city/cities) % and traffic (facility) % as
    high as possible to gain more money. Once you don't have enough money to buy
    anything the game is over and you can go back to the title screen."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
