  m_text: '- New Game -

    Starts a new game and leads you to the game screen


    -
    Select Game -

    This drop down menu appears when you have at least one saved
    game. The games are saved based on the the date (YYYY-MM-DD) you saved it.


    -
    Load Game -

    You can load a game if you selected a game slot, if there isn''t
    any saved games the button is disabled.


    - Quit Game -

    Quits from the
    application immediately.


    - Error Display -

    If there is any error/warning
    that was caused by the player or some funcionality isn''t available yet this
    displays it. You can remove it by clicking the X. '
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
