  m_text: "Welcome to the Transport Tycoon game!\nThis game simulates some features
    of the official Transport Tycoon\u2122 game.\nThe software developers: Ad\xE1csi
    B\xE1lint, Lajtai Benj\xE1min, Palotai Rich\xE1rd\nThis project aimed to implement:\n-
    Basic Logic\n- Minimap\n- Traffic Lights\n- Persistence (Save, Load)\n- 3D models"
