  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: '- Building Placer -

    This menu is placed in the top left corner and
    you can select which item you wanna buy (road, bus stop, traffic light and vehicles).
    When the game has started by default the mouse is selected. When an item is selected
    the price of the item is displayed and when you click on the map it is placed
    down (cars can only be placed on roads). If you want to sell any item you purchased
    select mouse and press shift (toggles demolish mode on/off) this activates demolish
    mode and by clicking on the object you sell it and the value is added to your
    balance.


    - Data Display -

    When a facility, traffic light, city or
    vehicle is clicked (Bulding Placer must have mouse selected) a display appears
    with the data of the object that was selected.


    - Minimap -

    In the
    top right corner you can find the minimap. The arrow in the middle points the
    direction where you are looking at the landscape.


    - Menu Bar -

    In
    the bottom left corner there is your account balance. In the middle you can find
    the time manager (Pause, Play, Forward, Fast Forward). In the bottom right corner
    you can see the in-game time.'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: 2180264, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
